T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"2020年都仲有人未睇過呢篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c7fd904547e66efdc2ec789e02fcdbf7332072","tid":1875724,"uid":40287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T05:54:00.000Z","msg":"失業潮文"},{"pid":"377510fcdd928959e3ec91479474e561da3de020","tid":1875724,"uid":48067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82bec86ed02cc4a853075196ea3704960a5f7169","tid":1875724,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:07:28.000Z","msg":"每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶 <br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網搵工, 每日SEND十封信差唔多, <br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂 <br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮 <br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少 <br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右, <br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活 <br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T05:56:57.000Z","msg":"拎埋 綜援  , 唔好只比新香港人拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死屎啦政府，一齊攬炒啦"},{"pid":"e6a9b561722c269a8854ca2bc0d8f4f3b8c0d7a3","tid":1875724,"uid":66449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T05:59:30.000Z","msg":"未禁入黎都估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f464467372ab5300d35dd6b86c48baf79eaecbb","tid":1875724,"uid":264988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aonBEto.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaonBEto.jpg&h=febf26fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6dcfd0cedb6575fd580976ee01582d69418f640","tid":1875724,"uid":94312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"樓主唔好灰心，試下apply樓下7仔先<i